{"tid":298876,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(香港太兒戲) 2015年,習近平到訪浙江省烏鎮,出動合共四萬軍警保護","createTime":"2017-06-26T15:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T15:36:15.000Z","uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b86af01dac9836ede101ff76fd6fb3ce9c4339be","tid":298876,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:26:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/12/%E3%80%90%E7%BB%84%E5%9B%BE%E3%80%91%E4%B9%A0%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%A4%A7%E4%BC%9A-%E5%9B%9B%E4%B8%87%E5%86%9B%E8%AD%A6%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E4%B9%8C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchinadigitaltimes.net%2Fchinese%2F2015%2F12%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25BB%2584%25E5%259B%25BE%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25B9%25A0%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E7%25BD%2591%25E7%25BB%259C%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BC%259A-%25E5%259B%259B%25E4%25B8%2587%25E5%2586%259B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2583%25A8%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E4%25B9%258C%2F&d=cHB5jyzH%2BO0d22hICkGRnlKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=efc7e430\" target=\"_blank\">http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/12/%E3%80%90%E7%BB%84%E5%9B%BE%E3%80%91%E4%B9%A0%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%A4%A7%E4%BC%9A-%E5%9B%9B%E4%B8%87%E5%86%9B%E8%AD%A6%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E4%B9%8C/</a><br />\n<br />\n中共當局為了萬無一失，只有一萬人口的烏鎮，部署了四萬多名軍警，當地的學校都變成臨時司令部。 <br />\n整個鎮方圓五公裡由武警部隊成土圓形包圍，街道上手持衝鋒槍的特警、武警及便衣警察密布，三步一崗，五步一哨，狙擊手亦准備就緒，連坦克、裝甲車也出動，防衛森嚴。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n軍佬進駐<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2015/12/1512141029022120.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F12%2F1512141029022120.jpg&h=3f68e026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n裝甲車進駐<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2015/12/1512141028472120.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F12%2F1512141028472120.jpg&h=fa7d1cd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坦克進駐<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2015/12/1512141030462120-600x334.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F12%2F1512141030462120-600x334.jpg&h=bee14ce6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n軍佬持槍戒備<br />\n<img src=\"http://bowenpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/5656560056c56baf560ff5656a565656f56c5656f56565656b56\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbowenpress.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F12%2F5656560056c56baf560ff5656a565656f56c5656f56565656b56&h=f787aae8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc5d7e2a6f2cd308838107a1241d1fb602233ea7","tid":298876,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:28:53.000Z","msg":"經中央軍委批準，從南京軍區調動一個裝甲團、一個特種作戰大隊，從陸軍航空兵調來一個直升機中隊；從海軍東海艦隊調來一個潛水中隊；以及一個地對空導彈營；加上一個武警機動師和浙江武警總隊(師級編制)，包括陸、海、空、導彈、武警四大軍兵種，全部兵力約4萬人。<br />\n<br />\n只有1萬居民的烏鎮，一下子湧入4萬軍警，有當地居民形容猶如「要爆發世界大戰」。<br />\n外國媒體觀察指，其安保嚴密，稱比北京「9&middot;3」抗戰勝利70周年大閱兵還嚴。一周前烏鎮開始戒嚴，野戰軍裝甲車部隊進駐外圍，從小鎮外幾公裡路口，武警即設卡檢查，鎮內幾乎每500米就有武警和公安站崗巡邏。<br />\n<br />\n空中有直升機轟鳴，地面有坦克裝甲車巡邏。海軍蛙人對鎮內河叉水底反覆搜查。防空導彈在鎮外高地虎視眈眈。小鎮入口要安檢，要進入會場須經3次安檢；若進入習近平現身的重要會場則須經第4次安檢，並持有更高級的通行證方可進入。為記者安排的兩間酒店大廳均安裝安檢通道，每次進入都由公安檢查。"},{"pid":"af788ac86bccb5f52343ac29e68ad4800169d643","tid":298876,"uid":69098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:36:15.000Z","msg":"你唔係以為到時冇共軍陀槍著便服係你側邊行過呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}